FBIS4-21912 "jptot015__l94077" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 6 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Hamas Carbomb in 'Afula Kills Eight, Wounds 50 Hamas Carbomb in 'Afula Kills Eight, Wounds 50 Near Bus Stop TA0604101494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1000 GMT 6 Apr 94 TA0604101494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] A powerful explosion caused by a car bomb occurred at a bus stop near the 'Afula Culture Palace. This has been announced by Commander Ya'aqov Ganot, the commander of the Israel Police Northern District Department. An initial report has four dead and about 10 injured. Our correspondent Yo'av Aviv reports that numerous Magen David Adom ambulances arrived to the site. No other details are available at this time.
